README for raytrace

    heagen/raytrace/
    heagen/raytrace/arftable/
    heagen/raytrace/eeftable/
    heagen/raytrace/xrtraytrace/
    heagen/raytrace/xrtreftable/

This directory contains the scripts and tools for raytracing.

- xrtreftable creates a reflectivity probability file for a telescope.

- xrtraytrace uses the reflectivity file from xrtreftable, and creates a photon
  history event file.

- arftable uses the history file from xrtraytrace and creates an effective area
  file.

- eeftable uses the history file from xrtraytrace and creates an EEF file.


